{"tid":220668,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【C朗涉強姦】德媒再爆料 740萬掩口費嫌貴壓價","createTime":"2017-04-28T06:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T08:29:50.000Z","uid":73092,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7631c9f356f887aed55a8077b494b1932ffeead9","tid":220668,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:40:11.000Z","msg":"德國《明鏡周刊》喺兩星期前爆料，指皇家馬德里球星基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）喺2009年夏天於美國拉斯維加斯強姦一名20歲女子蘇珊（化名），更令對方直腸受傷，最終以支付37.5萬美元（約292萬港元）掩口費了事。雖然C朗當時透過律師表示報道完全失實，純屬「傳媒創作嘅小說」，但《明鏡周刊》周四再度披露C朗喺2010年親筆簽署嘅庭外和解文件，顯示整份文件以「Topher」代表C朗，仲講明「有簽名有真相」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，該周刊亦聲稱擁有C朗同代表律師奧蘇里奧（Os&oacute;rio de Castro）嘅聯絡短訊，顯示C朗喺2010年得知被控後積極尋求庭外和解，當時對方開出95萬美元（約740萬港元）掩口費，C朗得知後大發雷霆表示費用過高，要求律師討價還價。"},{"pid":"a20ba52a943d156955fcc07fe5bcb03cf3a25e44","tid":220668,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"更令對方直腸受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9f14b7bce3e6749488b0d27bad0bc3b5301726","tid":220668,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"明鏡信唔信得過"},{"pid":"0d8667e5ba41fe723d7eb808bcb4bb1e4ef7ece6","tid":220668,"uid":19445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:40:39.000Z","msg":"屌穿腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45a92fc1ff017b9d91a98ce18c1b920f4dbf0a9","tid":220668,"uid":16306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"又逼害我朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab0587620e047cf34411deb06df6c8809d92e4a","tid":220668,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>更令對方直腸受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n強姦  姐係條女無事先準備啦  無灌腸<br />\n一幻想到插落入拔出黎成條撚都係屎就無晒胃口"},{"pid":"d3894bf01150